{
  "stem": "6773.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the ghetto, the only thing that I can remember were little anecdotes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I can sit here with you for-- for three weeks and tell you the stories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after the evacuation of my parents, three days later, when I found out that everybody is dead, we took to the bottle.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Liquor was always available.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Liquor was available in camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was from Pollocks, which they brought it in on black market.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to bring us liquor by the [INAUDIBLE] wagon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to take out clothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we use the exchange.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes we'll pay them additional cash, but we never ran out of liquor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Our period of over two years, I don't think there was a day that we should-- shouldn't have any liquor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And drinking-- I lived with five more people than-- except me-- we used to drink every day, at least [INAUDIBLE] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] fifths.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We had-- by breakfast, we used to have a fifth each one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just like drinking water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And money we had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, I had, and my group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But my brothers were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't have any money, but they had enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's like when the evacuation was from the whole ghetto, my friend, which lived beneath the ghetto, they put it a chief of staff of the camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They gave my brothers some jobs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They should go in and pick out the clothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, in the clothing, they found a lot of jewelry and all kind of-- all kind of money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's-- they had enough money, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But most of the people which worked in the factories, they didn't have no money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had a kitchen in camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
